comments: I tried to, but didn't originally. I started to notice patterns at the end of the game, but unsure if they were correct or just what the other party thought they were correct. I felt I had little time to strategise. I did not make notes. I found it difficult to see the spelling and the image at the same time as they weren't close enough together on my screen, so my eyes had to travel up and down for it, and I mainly had to rely on the sound which didn't help with the spelling. Learning the names by sound was easy.
